- New core/runtime_paths.py: resolve_data_dir() with write-probe per tier,
  loud failure when an explicit env override is unwritable
- PatternCache and DataLogger resolve lazily instead of hardcoding /data,
  fixing PermissionError on Codespaces and any non-root dev environment
- gitignore workspace-local ./data/
